Unfortunately, the high level game is raiding, not making friends or being super happy or whatever, you can do that at any level.  Naturally, being a casual gamer makes raiding harder, and makes raiding uber mobs extremely difficult.  If it's really that unfun, quitting isn't such a horrible idea.  The way uber mobs are designed, casual gamers will always be limited, none of the suggestions so far would really solve that.<br>
