<br>
There are a LOT of mobs in Velious that take hours of planning and practice to perfect. Some examples would be Dain, as I'm sure the people that were in Visions when they formed will agree, he takes a while to work out the strat for to kill, and you may fail quite a few times. The new Cazic Thule takes a refind strat to kill your first time as well, something that takes time.<br>
<br>
NToV can be the same, as it took the original guilds more then just a night to clear all of the dragons. Sure the content may seem like it's hard to come by, and it is. But it's not Verants fault, it comes from high end, &quot;powergamers&quot;, refining their strats for mobs and perfecting them for months.<br>
<br>
