<br>
Focking EQ is like a hobby in RL eg golf, football etc.  If u wanna do well in it u make sacrifices.  I know peeps who skive at work and hit the driving range juz to perfect that stroke.  Drawback is that if he is caught, he ass is fired.  Same goes for EQ, u wanna do good and see stuff in the endgame?  Be prepared to wake up at 4am to attend some raids for 3 hours b4 heading to work.  U can't or u won't do it?  Sux to be u.  I don't write to the newspaper forums and complain that my boss don gimme time off at work to perfect my Tiger Wood swing.<br>
<br>
Undoubtably Lanys will grow to be a overpopulated high level character server in time.  Most of the older servers are already having this problem.  Randomming spawn times will do jackshit to solve the problems cos powergamers will still adjust their lives to cope with the new system and get the mobs they want.  Casual players will still be fucked cause the random spawnings still does not fit into the 2 hour slot that they have.<br>
<br>
Read a post on top suggesting to verant coming up with a new server to host the top 5% of each server and make it triply hard.  Sounds like an idea but not too sure if it is feasible.  Heck I think VI can charge 20 bucks and still the powergamers will flock there.<br>
